research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Stanwood, WA operates under a mayor-council government. The elected officials include the Mayor and seven City Council members. Information on City Council Position 4 was found in a separate source. Recent articles from January 2026 mention Earl Cowan and Jeff Wheatley as new council members, but their specific positions were not explicitly stated in the provided snippets or consistently reflected in the primary staff directory at the time of this search. Therefore, the officials listed are based on the most explicit and position-assigned information available.
